===========
Description
===========

These are libraries to manipulate Geoserver (http://geoserver.org) files without 
interact with GUI or rest/wms/wfs calls. 
There are three managers:
  - UsersManager: manipulite users.xml, so manages users and groups  
  - RolesManager: manipulate roles.xml, so manages roles of users and groups
  - RulesManager: manipulate layers.properties, so manages relations between workgroups/layer and users/groups
  
PasswordEncoder is a simple utility to generate and encoded password for Geoserver.

Take a look in sample directory to see an example.

=======
Install
=======

This is a maven project so:

$ mvn clean install 

After that you will find egs-utils-2.0.jar in your maven directory.

